## 5. Security Checklist — Run Before AND After Assembly

Every check must return zero results. If any returns non-zero, the violation must be fixed before declaring Phase 7 complete.

```bash
# CF-01: No plaintext secret storage
grep -r "SharedPreferences\|prefs\.set\|prefs\.put" lib/
# Expected: zero results

# CF-03: No hardcoded URLs
grep -rn "http://\|https://" lib/domain/ lib/data/
# Expected: zero results

# AF-01: No Flutter in domain
grep -r "package:flutter" lib/domain/
# Expected: zero results

# AF-02: No cross-domain imports
grep -r "import.*auth_2fa" lib/domain/otp_gateway/ lib/domain/payment_observation/
grep -r "import.*otp_gateway" lib/domain/auth_2fa/ lib/domain/payment_observation/
grep -r "import.*payment_observation" lib/domain/auth_2fa/ lib/domain/otp_gateway/
# Expected: zero results for all three

# Invariant: No raw SMS body in any persistent structure
grep -r "rawBody\|smsBody\|rawSmsBody\|messageBody" lib/domain/otp_gateway/value_objects/ lib/domain/payment_observation/entities/ lib/domain/payment_observation/value_objects/
# Expected: zero results

# CF-04: No confirmation semantics in payment domain
grep -r "isConfirmed\|isApproved\|isPaid" lib/domain/payment_observation/
# Expected: zero results

# Full static analysis
flutter analyze
# Expected: No issues found!

# Full test suite
flutter test test/ --coverage
# Expected: All tests pass
```

