## 7. What You Must NOT Do

- ❌ Do not add any controls to the dashboard beyond pairing status display and unpair
- ❌ Do not skip the pre-assembly security checklist
- ❌ Do not add an auto-dismiss or countdown timer to the 2FA dialog
- ❌ Do not use the global navigator key for anything other than the 2FA dialog
- ❌ Do not declare Phase 7 complete if any security checklist grep returns non-zero
- ❌ Do not remove any `// TODO(phase-7-android):` marker — these are handoff points for the native Android engineer
